        When reseed is 0, tests the output of a temporary instance of an RNG against the expected output of size in bytes outputSz using the seed buffer entropyA of size in bytes entropyASz, where entropyB and entropyBSz are ignored.         outputSz - the output length.

        0 on success, < 0 on error.
